          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Oh... Are you really busy? Sigh. This letter needs to be delivered right away..."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh, the reply letter! Thank you! I want to give you something to show my appreciation."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Ta da! A hat! It has a level limitation, but I think you're strong enough to wear it. Thanks again for all your help!"
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "If you don't know how to equip items yet, open the #bEquip tab#k in your Inventory.\n You can freely switch between menus using the #bTab#k key. To equip an item, just #bdouble-click#k on it.\n To check if it's equipped properly, open the #bEquipment window#k."
        }
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirName": "stop",
        "_dirType": "sub",
