        "_dirName": "lost",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "You lost my reply letter? Bah, such carelessness! I have a town to run, you know. But fine, I'll rewrite the letter. Here, take it, and don't lose it this time."
